<body>
	<div id="aboutPageContainer">
		<h2>krdwrd help</h2>
		For you to be a productive drone, all you need to do is:
		<ul>
			<li>
				<b>select a corpus</b> using the krdwrd menu in your statusbar.
			</li>
			<li>
			    <b>grab a page</b> from your current corpus.
			</li>
			<li>
				<b>enable tagging</b> -
				Hovering over a webpage highlights
				the element under the cursor.
			</li>
			<li>
				<b>annotate</b>
				the currently highlighted element. Use the context menu to
				tag it.	The color will change accordingly.
			</li>
			<li>
				<b>submit</b>
				your annotation.
			</li>
			<li>
				<b>repeat</b>
				until you reach the end game monster.
			</li>
		</ul>
		<br />
		<i>
		Please note the keyboard shortcuts given next to the menu
		items. They tend to make life a lot easier.
		</i>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
